thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by John

author: John
title: John
text:
I typically purchase my frame from American Frame. I like their custom cutting - most of my prints (non paper) come back from the print lab slight off from the stated size (i.e. 20 1/8" x 30 1/16") so a "standard" frame will not work.
The ordering processing easy, the shipping is fast, and the frames are easy to assemble.
